      <p>Rocket Mortgage is the largest retail mortgage lender in the United States for a reason. Its fully digital application process is the most seamless in the industry, with real-time loan approval, a clean mobile experience, and robust customer support. Rocket's rates are competitive but not always the lowest - you pay a modest premium for the technology and convenience. Best for tech-savvy buyers who want a smooth, fast digital experience and strong customer service.</p>
 
